title: Championship Sunday Recap with NFL Super Friends (Football 1/21)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down the action from Sunday including the AFC Championship Game (2:00), the NFC Championship Game (34:30) and the Super Bowl matchup between the Patriots and Rams (58:00).
